{"tid":1034463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Amazon Prime Air 767係休斯頓附近墜機","createTime":"2019-02-24T02:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T04:38:11.000Z","uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"70949e914bf379c4f63e15f47d27e43d7095b01f","tid":1034463,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T02:50:25.000Z","msg":"A twin-engine Boeing 767 cargo jetliner operated by Atlas Air Inc. crashed into Trinity Bay near Anahuac, Texas, shortly before 12:45 p.m. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.airlive.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/x36938460640_7945805670_b-696x464.jpg.pagespeed.ic.G4tFL2Qt6U.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airlive.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2Fx36938460640_7945805670_b-696x464.jpg.pagespeed.ic.G4tFL2Qt6U.webp&h=1760381e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.airlive.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/xCapture-1-696x363.jpg.pagespeed.ic.DF5gEhr8rZ.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airlive.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2FxCapture-1-696x363.jpg.pagespeed.ic.DF5gEhr8rZ.webp&h=33f4e4a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.airlive.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/xPrime-Air-Boeing-767-crash-2-696x298.jpg.pagespeed.ic.MndzImTZAo.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airlive.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2FxPrime-Air-Boeing-767-crash-2-696x298.jpg.pagespeed.ic.MndzImTZAo.webp&h=c739b1b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.airlive.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/xPrime-Air-Boeing-767-crash-3.jpg.pagespeed.ic._qgWc2YIx0.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airlive.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2FxPrime-Air-Boeing-767-crash-3.jpg.pagespeed.ic._qgWc2YIx0.webp&h=e1b3348b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.airlive.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/xPrime-Air-Boeing-767-crash-4.